" I was working in the field when I heard the explosions of the earthquake , and I turned around and saw my house simply flatten in front of me ," said Fu Qiuyue , a 70 - year - old rapeseed farmer in Longmen . Fu sat with her husband , Ren Dehua , in a makeshift shelter of logs and a plastic sheet on a patch of grass near where a helicopter had parked to reach their community of terraced grain and vegetable fields .